  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency bel to v5",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel\">bel</a> from <code>v4.6.0</code> to <code>v5.1.2</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>shama/bel</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"512\">5.1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/82fb9adbf79a2a3d77f28f0d0c78112914888c4d\"><code>82fb9ad</code></a> 5.1.2</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/5308897c3abe0fcda3484ca4fdf01eea4c40d2ec\"><code>5308897</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;92 from graforlock/master</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/88d6eee8e7575f6b9398dee74c0bc89608df5140\"><code>88d6eee</code></a> Fixing raw export</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"511\">5.1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/6e7d42bef5675dda4123d8af9c00657eb757d81e\"><code>6e7d42b</code></a> 5.1.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/1011b026ee1605211c50befa997086f7346abdc2\"><code>1011b02</code></a> Merge branch &#x27;mauriciopoppe-master&#x27;</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/0edab8c54400a55afb230103d40405a2f5f3ca48\"><code>0edab8c</code></a> Explicitly disable offending rule</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/fc50adbdbe49175e82373ed096ca8301e14d0b56\"><code>fc50adb</code></a> fix(raw): server returns an instance of String instead of a primitive</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/a571c990df309be16fcf706f486cd5dddd5a4c64\"><code>a571c99</code></a> Fix download count badge</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"510\">5.1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/7a5d581ca80f666d3bc4d8892872e4e1d4fe47e0\"><code>7a5d581</code></a> 5.1.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/57bf0e06042e9033b1e8854daff74c36160f1638\"><code>57bf0e0</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;86 from jondashkyle/master</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/fe3351e388268ca11e7cfcdf1974cfa55b304e88\"><code>fe3351e</code></a> server and browser tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/15274ee69ef00797216dc605fca46b12ac1879fa\"><code>15274ee</code></a> removed unused var</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/664af5b68301291718f2e3d086c6a569e69bf041\"><code>664af5b</code></a> tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/48de24ece40bd35f961b426f10205656fc9edfd1\"><code>48de24e</code></a> docs</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/0464d16bd0a318349da5a17b102dc6142f1f182f\"><code>0464d16</code></a> raw</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"503\">5.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/30f210d2a7dac9519c5c4e327a7a8aedd3ae412c\"><code>30f210d</code></a> 5.0.3</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/01089332d0894b00f04d77dbbbe9ffffbc81a02f\"><code>0108933</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;85 from bcomnes/update-pelo</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/7759905ec806c4daeda6bc2663b26caa06ff9133\"><code>7759905</code></a> Update pelo</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/4322599116fb11cee9a5b56b67cfd4d1331258a2\"><code>4322599</code></a> Update devDeps</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"502\">5.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/687c3f814edbd2f872fc1864f17575e213c0aa24\"><code>687c3f8</code></a> 5.0.2</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/cc58e1ae5efb048127e5ffaaad1b1329ead51d5d\"><code>cc58e1a</code></a> Restore browser/electron handling (#&#8203;83)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"501\">5.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/faddb9f6483908e2359fcf46531c8fc262380f72\"><code>faddb9f</code></a> 5.0.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/4eda35dc09e75c5d1415cfe24a2a2dd726226088\"><code>4eda35d</code></a> Whitespacer (#&#8203;81)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/e9bd4048b9b8e69fa6633bf74371f59e9ad8d0ce\"><code>e9bd404</code></a> fix boolean properties for minification (#&#8203;82)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/2922e715b040790521a913fb0468de6fa826b01d\"><code>2922e71</code></a> use pelo (#&#8203;78)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"500\">5.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/5b0d458bb21ccb29cedf57cb6838825dc9a4802b\"><code>5b0d458</code></a> 5.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/3370966d515076a661b39b8f0697257606028d87\"><code>3370966</code></a> remove onload (#&#8203;76)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/9611b7f1f9895700be213036acce9734956850c5\"><code>9611b7f</code></a> add an object test (#&#8203;70)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/672ebabfeee46e9ab0b9303a2a0c91dcf216d54f\"><code>672ebab</code></a> fix whitespace creation (#&#8203;74)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"461\">4.6.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/3a05345fa880aed4ed91eb0dbf9293fff870d691\"><code>3a05345</code></a> 4.6.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/bel/commit/253d352f47e6fd09c69adeabf16a9a649a98133b\"><code>253d352</code></a> strip empty text nodes (#&#8203;68)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
